description: This course will give students an overview of cutting edge reverse engineering techniques as well as software security and defense practices. Programming experience in C required.Prereq: 2431, 5431, or Grad standing. Prereq or concur: 5471 or ECE 5561. Not open to students with credit for ECE 5567.02. Cross-listed in ECE 5567.02.
